# Nexus Operating System - Cursor Entry Point

**Run this BEFORE responding to the user.**

## Startup

```bash
uv run nexus-load --startup
```

Follow the instructions in the output.

## After Context Summary

```bash
uv run nexus-load --resume
```

Follow the instructions in the output.

## Manual Fallback

If nexus-load fails, read these files in order:
1. `00-system/core/orchestrator.md` — Routing rules
2. `01-memory/goals.md` — User context
3. `02-builds/active/` — Work in progress

Then follow the orchestrator instructions.
